commit.message:
Use a context manager to close the wordlist

Unittest will print a `ResourceWarning` for unclosed files.
Bump version to release changes for managing cython deps.

Support install without Cython already installed

The primary functionality change is that pip install ... should now work even in a fresh environment without Cython installed.

As of setuptools==18.0, Cython extensions can be built with just the Cython dependency specified in setup_requires. The direct import at the top of setup.py was preventing this behaviour as the import fails and terminates the code even though the Cython setup dependency was specified.

Support install without Cython already installed

The primary functionality change is that pip install ... should now work even in a fresh environment without Cython installed.

As of setuptools==18.0, Cython extensions can be built with just the Cython dependency specified in setup_requires. The direct import at the top of setup.py was preventing this behaviour as the import fails and terminates the code even though the Cython setup dependency was specified.

commit.message: Update version to 2.0.0 in the code too

Remove workaround for Python 3.0 to 3.2

We now require Python 2.x or >= 3.3.

Strip out epydoc mentions and support

epydoc has been dead for over a decade.

Fix function prototypes in .pyx file

The libstemmer prototypes were missing `const` and
PyUnicode_FromStringAndSize was missing `const` and using the wrong
type for the length.  In both cases this may have matched much older
versions.
Update installation instructions

Allow installing from git via pip

* Add a new distutils `bootstrap` command to download libstemmer_c (the
  URL and SHA256 can be overridden)
* The disutils `build` command now runs `bootstrap` automatically if
  libstemmer_c isn't already present locally
* Now you can do: pip install git+git://github.com/snowballstem/pystemmer

Based on changes from avikam-pagaya in #17.

Revert part of previous commit

Some pending changes were accidentally included.

Fix code style

Fix all pep8 default errors except for some about overlong lines.
Update to wrap Snowball 2.0.0

Changes list: 
- Use setuptools instead of distutils to handle `setup_requires` in `setup()`.

0 if a multiple of 256 tests fail.  Fixes github PR#10, but in a
slightly different way.
